MEDICAL ALTERNATIVES, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
AUTO-OWNERS INSURANCE COMPANY, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 158798
COA: 340561 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 28, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the November 1, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered and, it appearing to this Court that the case of W A Foote Mem Hosp v. Mich Assigned Claims Plan (Docket No. 156622) is pending on appeal before this Court and that the decision in that case may resolve an issue raised in the present application for leave to appeal, we ORDER that the application be held in ABEYANCE pending the decision in that case.
